### Reset both application records and vector evidence
POST http://localhost:8080/api/demo/reset

### Seed source records without indexing them
POST http://localhost:8080/api/demo/seed

### The application must return NO_EVIDENCE and skip the LLM
POST http://localhost:8080/api/assistant/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What should I do if failed sign-ins locked me out?"
}

### Make the approved support records retrievable
POST http://localhost:8080/api/demo/index

### The answer must cite policy-account-lockout-01
POST http://localhost:8080/api/assistant/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What should I do if failed sign-ins locked me out?"
}

### Clear vectors while leaving source records in place
POST http://localhost:8080/api/demo/vectors/clear

### Prove that source rows alone cannot ground an answer
POST http://localhost:8080/api/assistant/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What should I do if failed sign-ins locked me out?"
}

### Reindex the existing source rows
POST http://localhost:8080/api/demo/index
